Bimbo Ademoye, a budding Nollywood actress, has uploaded jaw-dropping images in celebration of her 31st birthday, which falls on February 4th, 2022. The actress took to Instagram to share images of herself looking stunning in a red and brown dress with a simple hairdo to match. READ MORE: Actress Bimbo Ademoye Celebrates Sola Sobowale On Her 58th Birthday Ademoye  says she’s in a good mood right now and hopes to stay that way forever as she wishes herself a happy birthday. She wrote: “Currently in a place called happy. I pray it remains this way forever”. See post below:   A post shared by Bimbo Ademoye (@bimboademoye) 